reviewText: We found 3 out of 10 tolerable. Seriously bad movie making, not just B movies, C, D, and F movies! Waste of time and money.

It shipped with a Broken DVD box will not close DVD. Guess you get what you pay for. Not again

the movies were good.
I didn't dislike any of them.
I would recommend these movies to anyone who likes to watch movies.

That is pretty much it.  My assumption about movies that would be put into an "Action Pack" is different.  All but one of these is dialog, dialog, dialog ....  dialog...  dialog...  swing, punch (an hour in) ... dialog ... "look out, he's got a gun" ... bang, you're dead ... dialog ... the end.

Ooooh.  "Action."
The price is excellent for good action packed movies. The movies are fun to watch while working out my treadmill or elliptical machine.  The workout time seems to go by faster and I feel better.

These are a great way to add to your dvd library. This is great merchandise.
I have done business with you before and no doubt will again. Thanks
This package gives me an excellent opportunity to see many of my favorite actors and their first rate performances in one place.
